PLATFORM CONTENT RULES
Platform Caption length Format Primary goal Instagram 1-2 lines + hashtags Portrait Reels, carousels Loyal community, saves Facebook 3-5 lines + question CTA Video, link posts Community groups, shares Threads Under 280 chars Raw thoughts, hot takes Conversation, relatability TikTok 1 line Vertical video Discovery, impulse 
--- 
CONTENT QUALITY FLOOR (MANDATORY CHECKLIST)
Before any content suggestion or brief is finalised: 
[ ] 3 L's passed — Lighting (natural), Location (non-distracting), Layout (product neat + intentional) [ ] No-sound test — story lands without audio [ ] FAN goal assigned — this piece serves Faithful / Advocate / or Nurtured [ ] Big Idea aligned — reinforces brand ideology, not just shows product [ ] System 1 score ≥ 3 — makes someone feel something in 2 seconds [ ] People in frame — at least one human wearing/using the product (no empty landscapes with quote overlays) [ ] Platform native — format matches the platform it's being posted to 